====Usage notes====
This character is not a modern Japanese character. It appears mostly in news reports of China or Taiwan issues, such as in reports about the Pan-Blue Alliance written as {{ja-l|泛藍連盟}} in Japanese news reports. The character {{ja-l|汎}} is the modern Japanese character which parallels this Chinese character in usage.

